Architecture

Client Layer

Browser extension or mobile overlay

Functions:
	•	tracker blocking
	•	signal masking
	•	product page detection
	•	price snapshotting

⸻

AI Analysis Layer

Detects pricing anomalies using:
	•	multi-profile comparisons
	•	statistical thresholds
	•	causal signal analysis
	•	pattern learning across merchants

⸻

Evidence Layer

Immutable pricing records:
	•	price comparisons
	•	environmental signals
	•	merchant history

Provides proof of discriminatory pricing patterns.

⸻

Merchant Side (Optional)

A voluntary API for sellers.

FairPrice Verify

Allows companies to certify they do not use:
	•	inferred income
	•	neighborhood wealth
	•	personal browsing history
	•	behavioral urgency signals

Certification badge:

“No Surveillance Pricing”

